{
  "stem": "17625.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They-- they-- they-- they came in-- German papers came in, there would be people who read from the-- from the other camps.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It wasn't-- It wasn't in a jungle, so we-- we knew it was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I interrupt, I bring something else out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I was brought back-- when I was brought back from Auschwitz to Birkenau to block two, before we went to 13, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] all of a sudden I heard the night shift, which was bunker still night shift.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They worked in bunker.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was coming from-- from-- from crematorium and I wasn't going with them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But bunker two came back at night shift, 12 o'clock, and they said there was a transport from [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they had some sandwiches.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I recognized the sandwiches from [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The way the bread was packed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my system with the kids were there, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in this-- in this-- in this transport, in the-- in the-- in the-- in the bunker.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was Purim.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Erev Purim, was it?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we sat and sing inside the Purim, you know, in-- in-- in the camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I remember even the song, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Know what I mean, the song?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was for Purim and my sister was there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This was-- this was Purim.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Other memories of that nature that happened during your time at Birkenau, other thing-- about the barracks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Didn't it get-- the Sonderkommando-- did more and more people die, was it lighter by the time you left-- lighter of people, fewer people?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I told you that they took out as-- as-- as transports rose, they brought in new people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As transports fell down, they eliminated people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They set all kinds of tricks, but we knew the tricks.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
